      <section eId="sec_28_5_107">
        <num>28-5-107</num>
        <content>
          <p>The board shall prepare and transmit to the General Assembly, along with its recommendation on each claim, a report of its activities in connection therewith, including the name of the claimant, a brief description of the facts surrounding the claim, the amount of compensation recommended, and the board's reasons therefor.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1967, p. 712, ยง 8.)</p>
